title: Mixing machine

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a mixing machine, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front-right side perspective view of a mixing machine showing my new design;
FIG. 2 is rear-right side perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front-left side perspective view thereof; and,
FIG. 4 is a rear-left side perspective view.
The broken lines shown in the drawings are for illustrating portions of the mixing machine that form no part of the claimed design.
